item.title: Playlist Generator
item.description: Playlist Generator An app that uses semantic search to generate afrobeat song playlists from input texts In the last year , ChatGPT changed the landscape of Artificial Intelligence and software engineering. This is why I and emmanuel offisong decided to build an app that made it easier to discover new afrobeats songs
